All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Article
The Article class represents an article entity in the article database table.
ArticleController
REST controller for managing articles.
ArticleRepository
The ArticleRepository interface is responsible for defining the methods that can be used to interact with the underlying database for the Article entity.
ArticleService
ArticleService is an interface responsible for defining the methods for retrieving articles from the underlying database.
ArticleServiceImpl
The ArticleServiceImpl class is a service class that provides methods to interact with the Article entity through the ArticleRepository interface.
Industry
The Industry class represents an industry entity in the industry database table.
IndustryController
The IndustryController class handles HTTP requests related to the Industry entity.
IndustryRepository
The IndustryRepository interface provides access to the industry database table.
IndustryService
The IndustryService interface specifies methods for retrieving and manipulating Industry objects.
IndustryServiceImpl
The IndustryServiceImpl class implements the IndustryService interface and provides methods for retrieving and manipulating
